ogy\"><code>&lt;feMorphology&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feOffset\"><code>&lt;feOffset&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/fePointLight\"><code>&lt;fePointLight&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpecularLighting\"><code>&lt;feSpecularLighting&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpotLight\"><code>&lt;feSpotLight&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feTile\"><code>&lt;feTile&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feTurbulence\"><code>&lt;feTurbulence&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font\"><code>&lt;font&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face\"><code>&lt;font-face&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-format\"><code>&lt;font-face-format&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-name\"><code>&lt;font-face-name&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-src\"><code>&lt;font-face-src&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-uri\"><code>&lt;font-face-uri&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/foreignObject\"><code>&lt;foreignObject&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>G\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/g\"><code>&lt;g&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyph\"><code>&lt;glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyphRef\"><code>&lt;glyphRef&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>H\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/hkern\"><code>&lt;hkern&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>I\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/image\"><code>&lt;image&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>J-L\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/line\"><code>&lt;line&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/linearGradient\"><code>&lt;linearGradient&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>M\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/marker\"><code>&lt;marker&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mask\"><code>&lt;mask&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/metadata\"><code>&lt;metadata&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/missing-glyph\"><code>&lt;missing-glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mpath\"><code>&lt;mpath&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>N-P\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/path\"><code>&lt;path&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/pattern\"><code>&lt;pattern&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polygon\"><code>&lt;polygon&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polyline\"><code>&lt;polyline&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>Q-R\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/radialGradient\"><code>&lt;radialGradient&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/rect\"><code>&lt;rect&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>S\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/set\"><code>&lt;set&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/stop\"><code>&lt;stop&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/switch\"><code>&lt;switch&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/symbol\"><code>&lt;symbol&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>T\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/textPath\"><code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>U\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/use\"><code>&lt;use&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>V-Z\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/view\"><code>&lt;view&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/vkern\"><code>&lt;vkern&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n   </ol></details></li>\n   </ol>\n  </section></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>marker-end</code></strong>&nbsp;属性将在给定<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element#shape_elements\">形状</a>的最终顶点绘制的箭头或者多边形标记。</p>\n\n<p>对于除 SVG 的 polyline 和 path 元素之外的所有形状元素，最后的一个顶点与第一个顶点相同。在这种情况下，如果 SVG 的 marker-start 属性和&nbsp;<code>marker-end</code>&nbsp;的值都不是&nbsp;<code>none</code>&nbsp;，然后再最后一个顶点渲染两个图标。&nbsp;对于一个&nbsp;<code>&lt;path&gt;</code>&nbsp;元素，&nbsp;对于每个封闭的子路径，他的最后一个顶点都与第一个顶点相同。&nbsp;<code>marker-end</code> 仅在<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/d#path_commands\">路径数据</a>的最终顶点上呈现。</p>\n\n<p><strong>Note:</strong>&nbsp;作为一个图像属性，<code>marker-end</code> 可以用作 CSS 属性。</p>\n\n<p>作为一个图像属性，他可以应用到所有的元素上，但是他只针对于一下其中元素有效: &nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/circle\"><code>&lt;circle&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/ellipse\"><code>&lt;ellipse&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/line\"><code>&lt;line&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/path\"><code>&lt;path&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polygon\"><code>&lt;polygon&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polyline\"><code>&lt;polyline&gt;</code></a>, and <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/rect\"><code>&lt;rect&gt;</code></a></p>\n\n<div id=\"topexample\">\n\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html; hightlight[12] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">viewBox</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0 0 120 120<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>defs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marker</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>triangle<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">viewBox</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0 0 10 10<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token attr-name\">refX</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">refY</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>5<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token attr-name\">markerUnits</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>strokeWidth<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token attr-name\">markerWidth</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>10<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">markerHeight</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>10<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token attr-name\">orient</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>path</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">d</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">fill</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#f00<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marker</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>defs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>polyline</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">fill</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>none<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">stroke</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>black<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token attr-name\">points</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>20,100 40,60 70,80 100,20<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">marker-end</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>url(#triangle)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"topExample sample\" id=\"frame_topexample\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/marker-end/_sample_.topexample.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用说明","title":"使用说明","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n   <td><code>none</code> | <code>&lt;marker-ref&gt;</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Default value</th>\n   <td><code>none</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"none\"><code>none</code></dt>\n <dd>表示将不会在终点绘制任何符号。</dd>\n <dt id=\"marker-ref\"><code>&lt;marker-ref&gt;</code></dt>\n <dd>这个值表示的是对 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/marker\"><code>&lt;marker&gt;</code></a> 元素的引用，将在终点绘制该元素.。如果引用无效，将不会绘制任何东西。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技术指标","title":"技术指标","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://svgwg.org/svg2-draft/painting.html#MarkerEndProperty\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) 2<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">marker-end</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Candidate Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>No significant change</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/painting.html#MarkerEndProperty\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) 1.1 (Second Edition)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">marker-end</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"svg.attributes.presentation.marker-end","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/marker-end/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另见","title":"另见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/marker\"><code>&lt;marker&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/marker-start\">marker-start</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/marker-mid\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">marker-mid (en-US)</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"使用说明","id":"使用说明"},{"text":"技术指标","id":"技术指标"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"另见","id":"另见"}],"summary":"marker-end 属性将在给定形状的最终顶点绘制的箭头或者多边形标记。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"marker-end","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/marker-end","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/marker-end/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/marker-end","title":"marker-end"}],"pageTitle":"marker-end - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}